                            <comment id="12447081" author="mprudhom" created="Fri, 3 Nov 2006 21:10:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed multiple problems with named queries: &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1. They were not being parsed as part of the or m.xml file, since we were incorrectly looking for an attribute named &apos;query&apos; (when it really should have been a sub-element named &apos;query&apos;). &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2. Looking for a named query did not force resolution of all metadatas.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;3. An NPE was being thrown when a JPQL query was created with a null filter&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
